&lt;p>Find Shelly devices on your network:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Adding Your First Device</title><link>https://tj-smith47.github.io/shelly-cli/docs/getting-started/first-device/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://tj-smith47.github.io/shelly-cli/docs/getting-started/first-device/</guid><description>&lt;p>This guide provides detailed instructions for adding your first Shelly device to the CLI.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites&lt;/h2>
